Version 0.3

    * Now you can speak only a selected text.
    * Interface is internationalized.
    * Check all languages eSpeak supports.

Version 0.4b

    * Issue 13 solved, an icon was added to the window.
    * Issue 12 solved, it was a translation problem.
    * Issue 14 and 16 solved, now GeSpeak can 'remember' some options.
    * Added an option to save output to a wav file.
    * Issue 15 solved, now languages' names are more user friendly.
    * Added amplitude option.

Version 0.4

    * Talk, Stop and Record buttons have images now.
    * Now GeSpeak stops talking before close.
    * Corrected some problems with file chooser dialog.
